discourse_list.title: Sienta.com - your source for RWA updates

content.content: Hey all, Long-time community member here. Super excited about all that is going on within the RWA onboarding – it is what will make Maker become the global (de)central bank. We have been looking for a single source of truth but struggled to find it, so hence we have built it. We will be compiling a weekly newsletter, updating on the latest news and latest projects that are being onboarded. please subscribe to get it!  https://www.sienta.com/ PS no spam ever - you have my word…
